descriptionHtml:
I always knew that Braith would be trouble when she got older.

Braith, a Ningheim Character Preset.

UPDATE: Braith is available as a follower in [url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/39532]PixeledVixens Ningheim Followers[/url]


[b]Required Mods:[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/35474/?]The Ningheim Race by Seren4XX HelloSanta Urshi and co [/url]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu by Expired [/url]


[b]Installation:[/b]
Download and open the text file.
Copy the text to your clipboard.
Enter the console and type \"showracemenu\"
Press \"F9\" to load the preset
author: PixeledVixens
